<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Yara duka, yara duka
 Yammata duk da maza
 Shi ku zo dai, sai ku zo dai
 Mu yi ta waƙa, mu yi ta waƙa.

[V2]
 2) Karɓi Yesu, karɓi Yesu
 Zai cece ku, zai cece ku,
 Zo, mu bi shi, zo, mu bi shi
 Ku karɓi Yesu, ku karɓi Yesu.</lyrics>
<title>Yara Duka, Yara Duka LW560</title>
